{"tid":1931422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"01：梁美芬舊將楊永杰「倒戈」戰九西　","createTime":"2020-03-18T07:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T09:00:28.000Z","uid":41404,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0a755de57444d0582eb59acb8d10d55e615d04fe","tid":1931422,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"據悉，已連續擔任四屆九龍城樂民區議員的楊永杰，有意出選九龍西，他前年年底已退出有份創立的西九新動力，今次「倒戈」與梁美芬對壘，聲稱要力爭「建制第四席」。<br />\n<br />\n楊永杰向《香港01》表示，積極考慮參選九龍西直選，並主攻所屬的九龍城區，他透露現時有約10名地區樁腳支持，有信心可取得最少3萬票當選。<br />\n<br />\n建制派人士分析，目前陣營內三大潛在候選人中，梁美芬的主要「票倉」在深水埗，陳凱欣則主攻中產屋苑較多的九龍城一帶，楊永杰出戰反而對陳凱欣的影響最大。"},{"pid":"afa38b6279cfcf6341f6d7065130b545e6b48132","tid":1931422,"uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"楊永杰表示，積極考慮參選九龍西直選，並主攻所屬的九龍城區，他透露現時有約10名地區樁腳支持，有信心可取得最少3萬票當選。（資料圖片 / 盧翊銘攝）<br />\n<br />\n楊永杰前年與另外五名地區兄弟退出有份創立西九新動力，包括：鄭利明、丁健華等，他坦言，退出是因不滿組織近年與經民聯越走越近，失去了當年代表獨立議員的取態。至於為何選擇今屆參選，楊永杰說，經評估實力後，認為自己有足夠地區樁腳支持，故不欲再為人「抬轎」，改由自己擔正出戰。<br />\n<br />\n現時九龍西6席中，4人為建制派，包括：民建聯蔣麗芸、鄭泳舜、經民聯梁美芬及無黨派陳凱欣，但蔣麗芸早前退出黨內初選，政界預料她不會競逐連任。"},{"pid":"28a3fb5d46d5d9c62a9d98ee1550afeff5fc8ac0","tid":1931422,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"Jeng"},{"pid":"70c9f21f5603ddd407a1cb60194de27bea50d80d","tid":1931422,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c2e8aad4fc18a96510fefd339a9f775e085227","tid":1931422,"uid":57674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢啲"},{"pid":"8b86b7d288fed220206e0446f1b1e61bb8de89a4","tid":1931422,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"中聯辦會聯絡佢"},{"pid":"d635b7ba01172ef9480673da6560c36d54553961","tid":1931422,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"3萬想選條毛<br />\n今鋪起碼要4萬先穩陣"},{"pid":"46cf56b179195690b53d75f79e05b0f235a7b61b","tid":1931422,"uid":41658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24c2e8aad4fc18a96510fefd339a9f775e085227","tid":1931422,"uid":57674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"放心啦，中聯辦一定搞鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda43660b970f0c5e2d6c8b435dbed8050753d64","tid":1931422,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"呢個保皇真係悉尼老鼠咩"},{"pid":"6160464f782a33d1ea2d469c5308d9e4bf9c24db","tid":1931422,"uid":313584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:18:13.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n輸梗<br />\n分分鐘界票界死自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8aa54e2735e941432d70ab3345193891a678963","tid":1931422,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"九西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱啱有新本土插咗旗 今次好睇啦"},{"pid":"0b316df993150a2f7dca58ab2c57c33b4883d13e","tid":1931422,"uid":23194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"最好啦屌"},{"pid":"4c5aca69a219f30dd5029905498446bbab15c133","tid":1931422,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b86b7d288fed220206e0446f1b1e61bb8de89a4","tid":1931422,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"中聯辦會聯絡佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3545f1d151270e4fa73df62b71ca2658ff69e889","tid":1931422,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"九龍城好藍<img src=\"/assets/fa